00:04:58.756 --> 00:05:01.556
&gt;&gt;They see the value in teamwork.

00:05:01.846 --> 00:05:03.196
&gt;&gt;Well, you can go put
Friday on that announcement.

00:05:03.726 --> 00:05:04.793
&gt;&gt;All right.

00:05:05.046 --> 00:05:06.976
&gt;&gt;Yay,

00:05:07.046 --> 00:05:07.306
&gt;&gt;Thank you!

